text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Symboli Rudolf's vice-president and<n>right hand,
Air Groove, worries for her<n>wellbeing since she
insists on balancing<n>her student council duties
with a<n>grueling training schedule.

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
The other vice-president, Narita Brian,<n>comes off
as blunt at first, but she<n>clearly cares for the
student council's<n>new general manager.

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Symboli Rudolf seems delighted to have<n>people
looking up to her. Over the<n>course of the day, I
catch a glimpse of<n>her relationships with the other
student<n>council members.
